Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十六簽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦  折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年看來會有好事發生呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是抽到末吉了吧？
